    <section class="godrej_properties" id="aboutscroll">  
        <div class="container">
            <div class="col-md-12 godrej_properties_content"> 
                <h2>About Embassy Projects</h2>
                <h4>Innovation, Sustainability, and Excellence</h4>
                <img alt="Embassy Group" class="img-fluid" data-src="images/about-embassy.webp" width="1920" height="679">  
                <p>Embassy Group, a leading development firm in real estate commenced its operations in 1993 led by Jitu Virwani, Chairman and Managing Director of the group. The establishment has developed 62+ Million Sq. Ft of Commercial, Residential, Retail, Hospitality, Services, Educational and Industrial Warehouse spaces and holds an extensive land bank of 1,000+ acres across the country. The operation spans across Indian and international markets that include Bangalore, Chennai, Hyderabad, Pune, Coimbatore, Trivandrum, Serbia and Malaysia.</p>
            </div>  
        </div> 
    </section>  
